Photo









Qualifying»






Two Hondas in Top Three in Argentina Qualifying

Honda claimed two of the top three spots on the grid for the FIA World Touring Car Championship Race of Argentina thanks to extremely strong performances by Norbert Michelisz and Tiago Monteiro.


